1
00:00:43,060 --> 00:00:46,780
=Auspicious Nobles=

2
00:00:47,580 --> 00:00:49,940
=Episode 18=

3
00:00:49,940 --> 00:00:52,500
(I'd Rather Be Your Kept Lover)

4
00:00:57,200 --> 00:00:57,880
Your Highness,

5
00:00:58,520 --> 00:00:59,710
the assassins are in position.

6
00:01:00,350 --> 00:01:01,560
If Li Qingqing is in danger

7
00:01:01,880 --> 00:01:02,750
and Jiuzhu appears,

8
00:01:03,200 --> 00:01:04,530
then she must be the Tower Master.

9
00:01:07,350 --> 00:01:08,350
Miss.

10
00:01:12,840 --> 00:01:13,590
Do it.

11
00:01:13,840 --> 00:01:14,280
Yes.

12
00:01:20,920 --> 00:01:21,510
Wait.

13
00:01:23,870 --> 00:01:27,070
Find out what that pendant is about.

14
00:01:28,430 --> 00:01:29,120
Immediately.

15
00:01:29,640 --> 00:01:29,950
Yes.

16
00:01:49,510 --> 00:01:50,400
Tower Master,

17
00:01:50,510 --> 00:01:51,710
just as you predicted,

18
00:01:51,790 --> 00:01:53,070
they've entered Noble Bank.

19
00:01:56,840 --> 00:01:57,430
Your Highness,

20
00:01:57,680 --> 00:01:58,430
we've found out.

21
00:01:59,620 --> 00:02:01,470
It was personally designed
by the Second Prince

22
00:02:01,480 --> 00:02:02,590
as a gift from Noble Bank

23
00:02:02,590 --> 00:02:04,000
for major depositors.

24
00:02:04,600 --> 00:02:06,780
The imperial merchants who do business
with him all have one as well.

25
00:02:10,710 --> 00:02:12,150
(So I misunderstood her.)

26
00:02:12,570 --> 00:02:14,760
(Thank goodness I didn't make
an irreparable mistake.)

27
00:02:17,680 --> 00:02:18,280
Let's go.

28
00:02:25,030 --> 00:02:25,680
Young Master,

29
00:02:25,700 --> 00:02:27,290
someone asked me to deliver this to you.

30
00:02:34,120 --> 00:02:36,080
(Wangshi secret workshop)

31
00:02:36,610 --> 00:02:39,430
(located three li west of Yinma Town
on the outskirts of the Capital.)

32
00:02:39,960 --> 00:02:42,280
(Hidden deep within a cliffside valley.)

33
00:02:42,590 --> 00:02:43,590
(Respectfully.)

34
00:02:44,310 --> 00:02:44,960
Investigate it.

35
00:02:45,960 --> 00:02:46,590
Yes.

36
00:02:55,430 --> 00:02:56,190
Tower Master,

37
00:02:56,360 --> 00:02:57,630
the little goal matter,

38
00:02:57,630 --> 00:02:58,860
I did a pretty good job, didn't I?

39
00:02:58,870 --> 00:02:59,770
Aren't you going to praise me?

40
00:03:00,310 --> 00:03:01,470
Praise you? Not a chance.

41
00:03:01,470 --> 00:03:02,630
This isn't over yet.

42
00:03:03,680 --> 00:03:04,630
Come here.

43
00:03:05,470 --> 00:03:06,280
In a moment,

44
00:03:06,400 --> 00:03:07,590
act like

45
00:03:08,190 --> 00:03:09,150
you're into me.

46
00:03:09,150 --> 00:03:11,280
Like you're always
finding excuses to get close to me.

47
00:03:11,910 --> 00:03:13,080
That way, he won't suspect

48
00:03:13,080 --> 00:03:14,590
we're close because we're accomplices.

49
00:03:14,870 --> 00:03:15,680
Got it?

50
00:03:16,030 --> 00:03:17,150
Do I really have to act?

51
00:03:17,910 --> 00:03:18,910
I really

52
00:03:19,870 --> 00:03:20,910
have feelings for you.

53
00:03:21,910 --> 00:03:23,470
Don't make me slap you.

54
00:03:23,710 --> 00:03:25,560
Did you understand what I just said?

55
00:03:25,750 --> 00:03:28,150
You mean playing a charming rogue
whose love isn't returned?

56
00:03:29,000 --> 00:03:29,590
Got it.

57
00:03:32,470 --> 00:03:34,120
What are you doing? I'll hit you.

58
00:03:34,430 --> 00:03:35,030
Don't move.

59
00:03:35,710 --> 00:03:36,630
My brother's here.

60
00:03:40,240 --> 00:03:40,960
Let her go.

61
00:03:43,560 --> 00:03:44,470
Your Highness,

62
00:03:44,680 --> 00:03:46,870
you said you wanted
to discuss business with me.

63
00:03:47,120 --> 00:03:47,710
But instead,

64
00:03:48,680 --> 00:03:50,120
you...

65
00:03:56,280 --> 00:03:57,150
Yuanzhao,

66
00:03:58,710 --> 00:04:00,590
as a prince, is it appropriate

67
00:04:00,590 --> 00:04:02,280
to use your status

68
00:04:03,710 --> 00:04:04,800
to pressure a young lady?

69
00:04:05,000 --> 00:04:06,870
The same goes for you, Yuanhe.

70
00:04:07,680 --> 00:04:09,630
I heard about the Spring Banquet.

71
00:04:10,150 --> 00:04:12,080
Let's not mock each other.

72
00:04:12,310 --> 00:04:14,520
At least I wouldn't force her.

73
00:04:16,270 --> 00:04:18,680
If you love someone,
you have to fight for them.

74
00:04:20,000 --> 00:04:22,310
If you're as hesitant
as you are, Yuanhe,

75
00:04:23,270 --> 00:04:25,600
I doubt you'll ever win her heart.

76
00:04:44,270 --> 00:04:45,750
(He insisted on walking me home.)

77
00:04:45,750 --> 00:04:46,880
(And he hasn't said a word.)

78
00:04:47,040 --> 00:04:48,430
(What is he trying to do?)

79
00:04:54,700 --> 00:04:56,580
(Pan Residence)

80
00:05:01,600 --> 00:05:03,570
Your Highness, we've arrived
at the Pan Residence.

81
00:05:04,620 --> 00:05:06,310
Thank you, Your Highness,
for escorting me home.

82
00:05:06,310 --> 00:05:07,390
I'll be going in now.

83
00:05:07,390 --> 00:05:08,070
Wait.

84
00:05:09,390 --> 00:05:11,070
I have something to say to Qingqing.

85
00:05:11,160 --> 00:05:11,750
- Yes.
- Yes.

86
00:05:11,780 --> 00:05:13,260
(Pan Residence)

87
00:05:20,870 --> 00:05:22,950
Your Highness, what else would you like?

88
00:05:24,310 --> 00:05:25,750
I've seen Pan Yang recently.

89
00:05:27,160 --> 00:05:28,630
While you're out running the household

90
00:05:28,630 --> 00:05:29,970
and managing the family business,

91
00:05:30,310 --> 00:05:31,920
you were nearly taken advantage of.

92
00:05:31,930 --> 00:05:33,950
Meanwhile, he's out
having fun with his concubine,

93
00:05:33,950 --> 00:05:35,190
without a care in the world.

94
00:05:36,040 --> 00:05:37,560
Why do you insist

95
00:05:38,070 --> 00:05:39,310
on keeping this title?

96
00:05:39,950 --> 00:05:41,920
It was my own choice.

97
00:05:41,920 --> 00:05:43,420
You needn't trouble yourself,
Your Highness.

98
00:05:45,630 --> 00:05:47,040
Do you think

99
00:05:47,870 --> 00:05:49,680
I'm supposed to just stand by and watch?

100
00:05:50,920 --> 00:05:52,560
Watch you in this mire,

101
00:05:52,750 --> 00:05:54,160
tormenting yourself

102
00:05:54,750 --> 00:05:56,000
and tormenting me?

103
00:05:57,560 --> 00:05:59,830
(You've read too many romance novels.)

104
00:06:02,000 --> 00:06:04,430
Your Highness and I
have nothing to do with each other.

105
00:06:04,830 --> 00:06:06,720
How could I possibly torment you?

106
00:06:11,120 --> 00:06:12,510
Since you refuse to divorce him

107
00:06:13,750 --> 00:06:15,920
and insist on remaining Mrs. Pan,

108
00:06:18,240 --> 00:06:21,190
I can stay by your side as someone
who must remain in the shadows.

109
00:06:23,480 --> 00:06:24,160
I

110
00:06:25,310 --> 00:06:26,920
am willing to be your kept lover.

111
00:06:32,750 --> 00:06:33,240
No...

112
00:06:33,950 --> 00:06:34,390
This...

113
00:06:34,390 --> 00:06:36,310
You're far too lovestruck.

114
00:06:36,480 --> 00:06:37,830
You're the Crown Prince,

115
00:06:37,830 --> 00:06:39,000
the future Emperor.

116
00:06:39,270 --> 00:06:40,800
Can't you come to your senses?

117
00:06:40,800 --> 00:06:41,600
Come on...

118
00:06:42,520 --> 00:06:45,910
♪Snowflakes settle gently
upon your brows♪

119
00:06:46,670 --> 00:06:50,050
♪Your dark hair
brushes across my fingertips♪

120
00:06:50,820 --> 00:06:52,560
♪Your smile♪

121
00:06:52,820 --> 00:06:55,110
♪Melts away the winter snow♪

122
00:06:55,110 --> 00:06:58,790
♪One fleeting glance says more
than a thousand words♪

123
00:06:59,250 --> 00:07:02,560
♪Yet I stand before you♪

124
00:07:03,300 --> 00:07:07,130
♪Unable to recognize your eyes♪

125
00:07:07,550 --> 00:07:09,470
♪Though fate tries♪

126
00:07:09,470 --> 00:07:12,050
♪To make us pass each other by♪

127
00:07:12,270 --> 00:07:14,640
♪I choose to make our story whole♪

128
00:07:14,680 --> 00:07:15,430
Yang,

129
00:07:15,630 --> 00:07:16,360
look.

130
00:07:16,560 --> 00:07:17,750
The carriage is rocking.

131
00:07:21,040 --> 00:07:23,310
Which shameless couple

132
00:07:24,430 --> 00:07:27,390
is fooling around
outside my Pan Residence?

133
00:07:28,870 --> 00:07:30,870
Let's see who's so bold.

134
00:07:34,310 --> 00:07:35,360
Which shameless pair is it?

135
00:07:35,560 --> 00:07:36,160
Come out!

136
00:07:37,750 --> 00:07:38,750
If he sees this,

137
00:07:40,000 --> 00:07:41,070
will he still want you?

138
00:07:49,510 --> 00:07:51,040
Getting into it, aren't you?

139
00:07:51,310 --> 00:07:53,310
Let's see how I deal with you today.

140
00:08:08,480 --> 00:08:10,120
Who are you going to deal with?

141
00:08:13,480 --> 00:08:14,270
Your Highness!

142
00:08:15,240 --> 00:08:16,240
I deserve death.

143
00:08:16,510 --> 00:08:17,750
I offended Your Highness.

144
00:08:17,750 --> 00:08:18,920
Keep your eyes shut.

145
00:08:19,800 --> 00:08:21,000
Until I give the order,

146
00:08:21,750 --> 00:08:24,190
if you dare open them, you die.

147
00:08:26,360 --> 00:08:27,630
- I won't.
- Yes.

148
00:08:57,240 --> 00:08:58,440
(Yuanzhao was right.)

149
00:08:59,320 --> 00:09:01,270
(If you love someone,
you should fight for them.)

150
00:09:08,720 --> 00:09:09,440
Let's go.

151
00:09:25,440 --> 00:09:26,270
Yang,

152
00:09:26,860 --> 00:09:28,840
Who do you think
was in His Highness's carriage?

153
00:09:28,840 --> 00:09:29,440
Shut up.

154
00:09:33,840 --> 00:09:34,550
Let's head back.

155
00:09:34,550 --> 00:09:49,100
(Pan Residence)

156
00:09:54,510 --> 00:09:56,150
What is going on today?

157
00:09:56,480 --> 00:09:58,150
Zheng Yuanhe
has completely lost his mind.

158
00:09:58,480 --> 00:09:59,670
Ptooey!

159
00:10:00,910 --> 00:10:01,960
Pour me some more water.

160
00:10:02,200 --> 00:10:02,910
Right away.

161
00:10:05,790 --> 00:10:07,480
Getting mixed up with that mad dog

162
00:10:07,500 --> 00:10:08,900
has brought me nothing but bad luck.

163
00:10:10,870 --> 00:10:11,720
Li Qingqing,

164
00:10:17,550 --> 00:10:18,720
when did you get back?

165
00:10:22,270 --> 00:10:22,910
What?

166
00:10:23,320 --> 00:10:24,670
Do I have to report to General Pan

167
00:10:24,670 --> 00:10:26,510
whenever I come home?

168
00:10:26,960 --> 00:10:29,550
Do I not even have the freedom
to leave the house anymore?

169
00:10:30,320 --> 00:10:32,320
Have fighting bandits
made you lose your mind?

170
00:10:32,350 --> 00:10:33,670
You really think you're somebody.

171
00:10:34,720 --> 00:10:36,240
Enough with the smart remarks.

172
00:10:36,790 --> 00:10:37,550
I'm asking you.

173
00:10:38,550 --> 00:10:40,120
One stick of incense ago,

174
00:10:40,360 --> 00:10:42,200
the Crown Prince's carriage
stopped outside.

175
00:10:42,670 --> 00:10:43,910
Where were you then?

176
00:10:44,210 --> 00:10:45,360
Were you inside the carriage?

177
00:10:45,480 --> 00:10:46,480
You're out of your mind.

178
00:10:47,480 --> 00:10:49,440
First, you accused me
of meeting some pretty boy.

179
00:10:49,440 --> 00:10:51,510
Now you're slandering
the Crown Prince and me.

180
00:10:51,600 --> 00:10:53,800
Why are you so obsessed
with accusing me of cheating?

181
00:10:54,320 --> 00:10:56,270
Then let me see
what shoes you're wearing.

182
00:10:57,600 --> 00:10:58,360
Let me take a look.

183
00:11:00,390 --> 00:11:01,510
Get away from me!

184
00:11:01,510 --> 00:11:02,510
You worthless scoundrel!

185
00:11:04,910 --> 00:11:05,790
Where are your shoes?

186
00:11:08,000 --> 00:11:09,750
You're the one
who's always fooling around outside,

187
00:11:09,750 --> 00:11:10,660
without a shred of shame.

188
00:11:10,670 --> 00:11:12,450
So you assume
everyone else is just like you?

189
00:11:15,650 --> 00:11:17,120
The shoes I saw on that woman earlier

190
00:11:17,120 --> 00:11:18,270
looked a lot like yours.

191
00:11:18,600 --> 00:11:20,150
Which eye of yours saw me

192
00:11:20,150 --> 00:11:21,450
getting into
the Crown Prince's carriage?

193
00:11:22,030 --> 00:11:24,000
Stop throwing false accusations at me.

194
00:11:24,010 --> 00:11:25,480
If you've got the nerve,
go ask the Crown Prince

195
00:11:25,480 --> 00:11:26,720
who was in that carriage.

196
00:11:26,720 --> 00:11:28,590
Instead, you come here
to throw your weight around.

197
00:11:28,600 --> 00:11:30,270
You bully the weak and fear the strong.

198
00:11:31,030 --> 00:11:31,790
I only asked.

199
00:11:31,790 --> 00:11:33,000
Why are you so worked up?

200
00:11:33,000 --> 00:11:33,840
Get out!

201
00:11:34,720 --> 00:11:36,200
The sight of you makes me sick.

202
00:11:36,240 --> 00:11:37,120
I'm warning you.

203
00:11:37,120 --> 00:11:38,070
From now on,

204
00:11:38,080 --> 00:11:39,810
don't come into my courtyard
without my permission.

205
00:11:39,820 --> 00:11:42,660
Otherwise, tomorrow I'll go to the Inspectorate
and beat the Drum of Grievance,

206
00:11:42,670 --> 00:11:44,870
accusing you of slandering
the Crown Prince and me.

207
00:11:45,000 --> 00:11:47,120
Let's see whether the Crown Prince
skins you alive first

208
00:11:47,120 --> 00:11:48,270
or tears my mouth apart.

209
00:11:48,600 --> 00:11:49,200
Fine.

210
00:11:49,510 --> 00:11:50,480
I'll leave, all right?

211
00:11:50,720 --> 00:11:51,390
Get out!

212
00:11:52,080 --> 00:11:53,360
Crazy woman.

213
00:11:53,600 --> 00:11:54,440
Watch what you say.

214
00:11:54,440 --> 00:11:54,960
Get out!

215
00:12:10,840 --> 00:12:14,000
Why does this feel like
I'm about to get caught?

216
00:12:15,910 --> 00:12:18,360
That Zheng Yuanhe is my natural nemesis.

217
00:12:22,320 --> 00:12:22,870
Your Highness,

218
00:12:23,000 --> 00:12:24,080
I don't understand.

219
00:12:24,120 --> 00:12:26,750
Why are you helping the Crown Prince
find Wangshi Tower's workshop?

220
00:12:27,720 --> 00:12:29,790
Those clever little schemes of hers

221
00:12:30,410 --> 00:12:32,200
aren't enough
to bring down my dear brother.

222
00:12:33,150 --> 00:12:34,720
She needs to be ruthless.

223
00:12:35,200 --> 00:12:37,750
Give her a reason
she has no choice but to kill him.

224
00:12:38,080 --> 00:12:40,270
Then why did Your Highness
help Li Qingqing just now?

225
00:12:42,600 --> 00:12:43,720
Next...

226
00:12:44,870 --> 00:12:46,200
We'll set a fire

227
00:12:46,720 --> 00:12:47,960
and burn down the bank.

228
00:12:48,270 --> 00:12:48,870
Your Highness,

229
00:12:49,000 --> 00:12:50,790
there's a lot of our money in there.

230
00:12:51,120 --> 00:12:52,870
Which one of us
do you think is the fool?

231
00:12:54,080 --> 00:12:56,000
Quietly have someone withdraw the money.

232
00:12:56,550 --> 00:12:57,480
Then burn it down

233
00:12:57,840 --> 00:12:59,440
and pin it on Zheng Yuanhe.

234
00:13:00,270 --> 00:13:01,480
That way,

235
00:13:02,440 --> 00:13:04,030
she'll hate him

236
00:13:04,510 --> 00:13:05,510
even more.

237
00:13:06,720 --> 00:13:08,320
(Qingqing.)

238
00:13:09,030 --> 00:13:10,320
(You are clever.)

239
00:13:10,870 --> 00:13:12,240
(You're just not ruthless enough.)

240
00:13:12,910 --> 00:13:14,790
(Let me help you with that.)

241
00:13:21,010 --> 00:13:24,370
♪Snowflakes settle gently
upon your brows♪

242
00:13:25,130 --> 00:13:28,530
♪Your dark hair
brushes across my fingertips♪

243
00:13:29,290 --> 00:13:31,050
♪Your smile♪

244
00:13:31,290 --> 00:13:33,570
♪Melts away the winter snow♪

245
00:13:33,570 --> 00:13:37,250
♪One fleeting glance says more
than a thousand words♪

246
00:13:37,730 --> 00:13:41,050
♪Yet I stand before you♪

247
00:13:41,770 --> 00:13:45,610
♪Unable to recognize your eyes♪

248
00:13:46,010 --> 00:13:47,930
♪Though fate tries♪

249
00:13:47,930 --> 00:13:50,530
♪To make us pass each other by♪

250
00:13:50,730 --> 00:13:54,170
♪I choose to make our story whole♪

251
00:13:54,410 --> 00:13:56,050
♪Though time slips by♪

252
00:13:56,050 --> 00:13:57,810
♪As day turns into night♪

253
00:13:58,330 --> 00:14:02,370
♪I still remember
our days at Wangshi Tower♪

254
00:14:02,770 --> 00:14:05,170
♪One glance at you lasts a lifetime♪

255
00:14:05,170 --> 00:14:06,930
♪Blessed by fate♪

256
00:14:06,930 --> 00:14:12,090
♪I believe this moment
will last forever♪

257
00:14:12,090 --> 00:14:14,530
♪Your smiling face♪

258
00:14:14,530 --> 00:14:17,370
♪Is the most beautiful poem♪

259
00:14:17,370 --> 00:14:21,010
♪I'd rather spend my days with you♪

260
00:14:21,530 --> 00:14:24,970
♪And wander the world together♪

261
00:14:24,970 --> 00:14:26,330
♪Holding you close♪

262
00:14:26,330 --> 00:14:28,850
♪Envying neither lovers nor immortals♪

263
00:14:28,850 --> 00:14:31,170
♪Your tenderness♪

264
00:14:31,170 --> 00:14:34,050
♪Is the brightest moon♪

265
00:14:34,050 --> 00:14:37,730
♪I'd rather
pledge three lifetimes to you♪

266
00:14:38,250 --> 00:14:41,570
♪Our love will never fade away♪

267
00:14:41,570 --> 00:14:44,010
♪Though heaven and earth grow old♪

268
00:14:44,530 --> 00:14:48,810
♪My heart will remain forever pure♪

269
00:14:58,290 --> 00:15:00,450
♪Your smiling face♪

270
00:15:00,610 --> 00:15:03,210
♪Is the most beautiful poem♪

271
00:15:03,530 --> 00:15:07,370
♪I'd rather spend my days with you♪

272
00:15:07,610 --> 00:15:11,090
♪And wander the world together♪

273
00:15:11,090 --> 00:15:12,410
♪Holding you close♪

274
00:15:12,410 --> 00:15:15,050
♪Envying neither lovers nor immortals♪

275
00:15:15,050 --> 00:15:17,330
♪Your tenderness♪

276
00:15:17,330 --> 00:15:20,170
♪Is the brightest moon♪

277
00:15:20,170 --> 00:15:23,930
♪I'd rather
pledge three lifetimes to you♪

278
00:15:24,370 --> 00:15:27,730
♪Our love will never fade away♪

